r, Cache) using Docker Compose for consistent development and\ndeployment environments. [GitHub]\nTrue Feedback - AI-Powered Feedback Platform | Next.js, TypeScript, MongoDB\nOct 2025 – Oct 2025\n– Developed an anonymous feedback platform with unique public links, built using Next.js and TypeScript.\n– Implemented authentication with NextAuth.js (email/password + Google OAuth) and integrated Google Gemini\nAI for intelligent message suggestions.\n– Engineered a private dashboard for real-time message management, ensuring end-to-end integrity with Zod\nvalidation and Resend email verification. [GitHub]\nCampus Forum - Full-Stack MERN Application | React, Node.js, MongoDB\nAug 2025 – Sep 2025\n– Architected a MERN forum for academic discussions with RESTful APIs supporting all CRUD operations.\n– Implemented secure, role-based authentication (User/Admin) using JWT with access/refresh tokens in\nHTTP-only cookies.\n– Developed an admin dashboard for user/content management and a dynamic analytics page to track\nregistrations and content creation. [GitHub]\nEducation\nBachelor of Computer Applications\nJuly 2023 - April 2026 (Expected)\nS S Agrawal College, Navsari (Affiliated with VNSGU)\nCGPA: 9/10\nHSC (12th Grade)\nMarch 2023\nR. D. Patel Sarvajanik Vidyalay (GSEB)\nPercentage: 85.2%\n')
